oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Webb Pierce: "Christmas At Home" Hey
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Cedarwood Publishing Company; Guitar; Musical instruments; Pierce, Webb, 1921-1991; Offset printing;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color offset printing plate (red on silver) advertising watch for the Christmas hit of the year -- Webb Pierce's song "Christmas At Home," written by Max Powell and Wayne Walker, coming in November on Decca. The plate features two photographs of Webb Pierce.
